Package kieker.tools.trace.analysis.filter.visualization.graph

Class CompleteOriginRetentionPolicy

java.lang.Object
kieker.tools.trace.analysis.filter.visualization.graph.AbstractOriginRetentionPolicy
kieker.tools.trace.analysis.filter.visualization.graph.CompleteOriginRetentionPolicy
All Implemented Interfaces:
IOriginRetentionPolicy
public final class CompleteOriginRetentionPolicy
extends AbstractOriginRetentionPolicy
The complete origin retention policy represents the intention that every origin should be retained in the graph model and corresponds to the kind OriginRetentionPolicyKind.ALL. Be aware that this policy may lead to extensive resource consumption when processing vast logs.
Since:
1.6
Author:
Holger Knoche
